msgstr ""

#: ../../comprules.rst:7832
msgid "702.15b"
msgstr ""

#: ../../comprules.rst:7833
msgid ""
"Damage dealt by a source with lifelink causes that source's controller, or "
"its owner if it has no controller, to gain that much life (in addition to "
"any other results that damage causes). See rule :ref:`119.3 <mtgcr-119-3>`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../comprules.rst:7838
msgid "702.15c"
msgstr ""

#: ../../comprules.rst:7839
msgid ""
"If a permanent leaves the battlefield before an effect causes it to deal "
"damage, its last known information is used to determine whether it had "
"lifelink."
msgstr ""

#: ../../comprules.rst:7844
msgid "702.15d"
msgstr ""

#: ../../comprules.rst:7845
msgid ""
"The lifelink rules function no matter what zone an object with lifelink "
"deals damage from."
msgstr ""

#: ../../comprules.rst:7850
msgid "702.15e"
msgstr ""

#: ../../comprules.rst:7851
msgid "Multiple instances of lifelink on the same object are redundant."
